---
title: Chermoula Crumbed Pork & Radish Salad with Roast Chilli Garlic Pumpkin
description: Schnitzel and wedges is a pub classic that we’ll never get tired of - but who’s ready for a delicious new twist? We are!
This golden pork schnitzel has the flavours of the Middle East cooked right into the crumb. As if that wasn’t enough,
pumpkin wedges baked in a chilli garlic butter are our new favourite accompaniment.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65f27eb72d32e2180f38fcff-56542261.jpeg
